1
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:37,920
Who is it?

2
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:40,040
Miss Ye told me to bring you some clothes.

3
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:42,920
At least she has some conscience.

4
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:55,719
Why is it you again?

5
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:57,799
Hand over the Sea Suppressor Manual.

6
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:58,400
And I'll spare your life.

7
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:00,439
What Suppressor? What Manual?

8
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:02,159
I really have no idea.

9
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,319
Stop pretending.

10
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,159
Do you know how many people out there

11
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:09,520
are hunting for Number Zero, the thief of

12
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,280
the Sea Suppressor Manual?

13
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:14,479
I'm just a lowly country doctor.

14
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:16,360
Where would I get that kind of skill

15
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,560
to steal any secret manual?

16
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,479
A lowly country doctor?

17
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:22,439
The Mother-Child Yin-Yang Gu

18
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:24,039
is a forbidden Gu in ancient Gu arts.

19
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:27,919
I've never seen anyone suppress its venom.

20
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,240
But you,

21
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,599
three times in a row,

22
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:34,639
helped me suppress the Gu venom attacks.

23
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,360
You're quite impressive.

24
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,599
I guess I'm okay.

25
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,240
Is this how you treat your lifesaver?

26
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,080
How rude.

27
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:57,240
Just hand over the Sea Suppressor Manual,

28
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:59,719
and since you saved my life a few times,

29
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:01,120
I'll help hide your identity

30
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,719
and spare your life.

31
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,120
How about this:

32
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,639
I can completely cure the Gu venom in you.

33
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:11,360
You quit this job of yours,

34
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,879
and then you won't have to kill me.

35
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:13,159
Please, I'm begging you.

36
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:21,400
Director Ye, what brings you here so late?

37
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:23,520
I heard

38
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,120
some noise in your room.

39
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:30,319
I was just training a bit too intensely.

40
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,719
Director Ye, I have good news.

41
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:37,800
I've mastered the Sea Suppressor Manual.

42
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:38,800
That fast?

43
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,759
Of course.

44
00:03:39,759 --> 00:03:41,000
Do you know who I am?

45
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,039
Director Ye, you should rest early.

46
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:44,599
I'll keep refining my skills.

47
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,199
Goodbye, Director Ye.

48
00:03:47,199 --> 00:03:48,120
Goodnight, Director Ye.

49
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,120
You've mastered the Sea Suppressor Manual.

50
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,319
This is for you.

51
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,839
Let me give you a piece of advice.

52
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:37,600
The Gu venom has reached your dantian.

53
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,759
If you keep stalling,

54
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:41,800
no matter how great my medical skills,

55
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,519
your body simply won't hold up.

56
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:47,319
Why throw your life away

57
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,720
for such a vicious master?

58
00:05:09,639 --> 00:05:10,680
None of your business.

59
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,560
So...

60
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,560
Are you sure you were just talking to yourself?

61
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,600
I'm just being dedicated to my work.

62
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:38,920
Practicing my lines.

63
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,560
And getting some exercise too.

64
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,399
You should get going. Head back now.

65
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,319
Anything else?

66
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,319
Take care, I won't see you out.

67
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:05,759
What a day.

68
00:06:16,279 --> 00:06:18,560
Found Zero and the Sea Suppressor Manual?

69
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:24,560
Why throw your life away

70
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,879
for such a vicious master?

71
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,120
I have failed you.

72
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,160
We found nothing.

73
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:31,680
Useless.

74
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,360
Ye Qingxue is also looking for Zero.

75
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,240
She collected Zero's fingerprints.

76
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:43,360
But the records show no such person.

77
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,560
I'll spare you one more time.

78
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:02,199
No Zero or Sea Suppressor Manual again,

79
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:04,399
you know the consequences better than me.

80
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:30,920
What are you doing?

81
00:07:31,839 --> 00:07:33,120
This is your fiancé?

82
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,319
What a headache.

83
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:35,839
Do whatever you want with him.

84
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,319
Saggy skin.

85
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:49,319
Enlarged pores.

86
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,839
Excess oil.

87
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:53,319
And this scrawny figure, no good either.

88
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,000
Ye Qingxue, save me!

89
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:03,600
You said you'd be the Dragon King's groom.

90
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:06,199
I was just saying it offhand.

91
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:07,360
How could you take it seriously?

92
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:10,519
Well, I did.

93
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,160
Director Ye!

94
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:17,879
Don't leave!

95
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:20,519
Director Ye, where are you going?

96
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:21,839
Come on.

97
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:22,720
Pull him up.

98
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:23,839
What are you doing?

99
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:24,519
Stop taking pictures!

100
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,000
Give us a smile.

101
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,720
Smile a little.

102
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,600
Expressions.

103
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,319
Change your pose.

104
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,920
Am I going to a pharmacist exam,

105
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,399
or a beauty pageant?

106
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,919
Help!

107
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:55,320
Welcome to Cheng Qi's

108
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,559
private wardrobe.

109
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,279
This overall look isn't bad.

110
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,799
What are you doing? I'm warning you!

111
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:28,600
I'd rather die than take off my underwear!

112
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,240
This is my ride-or-die buddy.

113
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,240
My absolute bottom line.

114
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,440
Seriously?

115
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,720
Honestly, if it weren't for Director Ye,

116
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,759
I wouldn't bother with you at all.

117
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:42,360
Today I'll show you what a true collection is.

118
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,240
This is from the famous designer

119
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:48,759
Maosang Pierre's runway piece this year.

120
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,440
Come on.

121
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,639
Four sleeves? How am I supposed to wear this?

122
00:09:52,639 --> 00:09:54,840
Director Ye, why not lend me two arms?

123
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:55,840
We'll try it together.

124
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,519
If you don't put it on right now,

125
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,720
I'll make sure you have no arms left.

126
00:10:16,039 --> 00:10:17,320
Are you sure dressed like this,

127
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:19,960
I won't be caged as a jellyfish?

128
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,000
Country bumpkin.

129
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,799
How about this one?

130
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:39,679
Get out here!

131
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:48,440
I'm still pretty conservative, you know.

132
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:50,000
Director Ye, don't hold such a grudge.

133
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,799
This outfit actually shows off a nice physique.

134
00:10:58,559 --> 00:10:59,360
Of course it does.

135
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:02,639
Let me show you

136
00:11:02,639 --> 00:11:04,399
what real fashion looks like.

137
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:26,200
How do designer brands

138
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,320
end up looking like a QQ avatar on you?

139
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,240
What do you know?

140
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,519
This is chic night-walker style.

141
00:11:30,519 --> 00:11:31,639
Walking down the street in this outfit,

142
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:32,919
you wouldn't even need streetlights.

143
00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:34,039
You're hopeless.

144
00:11:35,279 --> 00:11:35,879
Just wait.

145
00:11:36,679 --> 00:11:37,879
There's an even bigger surprise.

146
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,440
My entrance will steal the entire show.

147
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,639
I'm about to blind you with my brilliance.

148
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:20,159
Your decade-old West Coast taste

149
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:21,120
really needs an emergency rescue.

150
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,440
Should I book you an eye doctor?

151
00:12:24,799 --> 00:12:26,799
Still better than those rags you picked!

152
00:12:33,799 --> 00:12:35,000
Get lost!

153
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,120
How is it?

154
00:13:18,919 --> 00:13:21,240
Were you electrified by my charm?

155
00:13:24,159 --> 00:13:25,759
Passable, I guess.

156
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,000
Wipe it carefully.

157
00:13:40,879 --> 00:13:41,679
Well, did you wipe it?

158
00:13:41,679 --> 00:13:42,440
Yes, I did.

159
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,519
Everyone, please gather in the main hall.

160
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:56,320
This is the pharmacist consultant I hired.

161
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,480
Who is this guy?

162
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,039
I've never seen him before.

163
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,559
Didn't he cause a scene at the pharmacy?

164
00:14:02,559 --> 00:14:03,879
I have to say, he's pretty handsome.

165
00:14:03,879 --> 00:14:04,840
Being handsome doesn't mean anything.

166
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:07,440
He probably knows Director Ye.

167
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,360
Could he be Director Ye's boyfriend?

168
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,320
No way.

169
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:14,559
He really is quite handsome.

170
00:14:14,559 --> 00:14:16,279
But why does he look so familiar?

171
00:14:16,279 --> 00:14:17,559
He probably just knows Director Ye.

172
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:21,720
Consultant?

173
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:25,200
Thinks a new shell makes a turtle a god?

174
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,639
Isn't he just the apothecary boy I fired?
